			<p>
			we are <strong><code>&lt;weak&gt;idktheflag&lt;/weak&gt;</code></strong>
            </p>
			<p>
			ms paint logo go brrr<br>
			caffeine addict team
            </p>
            
            <h2>The Roster</h2>
            <ul class="roster-list">
				<li><img src="/pfps/riverxia.png" alt="riverxia" class="roster-pfp" /><strong>(C) <a href="/team/riverxia"><i>riverxia</i></a></strong> — legit everything lol (carry w)</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/quickshot.png" alt="qu1ck5h0t" class="roster-pfp" /><strong>(C) <a href="/team/qu1ck5h0t"><i>qu1ck5h0t</i></a></strong> — cryptography</li>
